    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Perennial plants which have no woody stem, and which can be divided into three types: annuals, biennials, and herbaceous perennials. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
